{"tid":1094920,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想知有冇人住公屋會偷偷地養狗","createTime":"2019-04-06T16:11:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T05:59:34.000Z","uid":202044,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bce5c51f6c1b214df280ecae8acb185f528b1192","tid":1094920,"uid":202044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T16:11:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9cc39a395981e86400e58f7bb03273973bb0a35f","tid":1094920,"uid":161734,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T16:26:57.000Z","msg":"知鄰居有 不過細狗嚟 平時好少叫 出入放狗會好小心 其實唔影響到人其實冇咩問題 同埋聽講有得申請養"},{"pid":"ed4cd2f2ccb2a07e627c56f894a0a18aaacca44b","tid":1094920,"uid":202044,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"9cc39a395981e86400e58f7bb03273973bb0a35f","tid":1094920,"uid":161734,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T16:26:57.000Z","msg":"知鄰居有 不過細狗嚟 平時好少叫 出入放狗會好小心 其實唔影響到人其實冇咩問題 同埋聽講有得申請養"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:08:43.000Z","msg":"其實係咪只要唔影響到鄰居就冇咩問題？<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"570684af168a0f8064d1c9e1fb8ed05f1d89c7b6","tid":1094920,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:12:31.000Z","msg":"大把<br />\n<br />\n樓下有個阿伯夏天成日唔著衫落去放狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n通常細細隻買返嚟，訓練到唔識叫，其實啲狗好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5ebce3709334c431110227cd9404205501a7f0","tid":1094920,"uid":63303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed4cd2f2ccb2a07e627c56f894a0a18aaacca44b","tid":1094920,"uid":202044,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"9cc39a395981e86400e58f7bb03273973bb0a35f","tid":1094920,"uid":161734,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T16:26:57.000Z","msg":"知鄰居有 不過細狗嚟 平時好少叫 出入放狗會好小心 其實唔影響到人其實冇咩問題 同埋聽講有得申請養"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:08:43.000Z","msg":"其實係咪只要唔影響到鄰居就冇咩問題？<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:16:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/public-housing/estate-management/marking-scheme-for-estate-management-enforcement/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic-housing%2Festate-management%2Fmarking-scheme-for-estate-management-enforcement%2Findex.html&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYj4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=024bba9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/public-housing/estate-management/marking-scheme-for-estate-management-enforcement/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n房屋署會採取「可暫准原則」，處理在扣分制實施前已在公屋飼養的狗隻。根據有關原則，在2003年8月1日前已在公屋飼養的小型狗隻 (即體重少於20公斤的狗隻)，租戶必須事先獲得一次過批准，才可繼續飼養狗隻。獲批准的租戶須嚴格遵守署方訂定的守則，租戶如兩次違反飼養狗隻的守則，有關批准便會被撤銷。<br />\n<br />\n由2003年11月1日開始，租戶未經業主書面同意，在租住單位飼養狗隻或被禁止的動物，將會按扣分制被扣分。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n03年前養落嘅可以申請繼續養，之後唔准養新狗"},{"pid":"39e92149314062f20456cf9503a6024fe4ea3751","tid":1094920,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:20:24.000Z","msg":"鄰居有隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地仲要係呢1,2年先養 <br />\n隻狗日日係咁吠 都係冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a94722e97484d3d6f269c89bf98ce6ec967193","tid":1094920,"uid":93649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:24:21.000Z","msg":"大撚把 搞到附近全地狗屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做番個有責任感既狗主都唔得<br />\n不過夜晚好多狗主都光明正大帶狗落街行<br />\n同埋會同其他狗主人傾 見d狗互相玩都幾開心<br />\n同埋房處都冇撚用架啦"},{"pid":"0edb1dad886fa4acb17f063e9478df662e522af8","tid":1094920,"uid":81253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T17:27:24.000Z","msg":"對面屋有養 不過隻狗係狗場救返黎同埋俾狗場果邊割左聲帶 所以唔會嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d0f11a482c0cb4ce5bc6722a7010f4b085b4c4","tid":1094920,"uid":198541,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T11:53:06.000Z","msg":"只要你肯投訴就幫到d狗，要令社會知道偷養係會冇屋住先係幫到d狗"},{"pid":"c5da2bfd28eed82fcfa1d8c0dca53ae08641ff30","tid":1094920,"uid":202044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:22:24.000Z","msg":"因為小弟好中意狗想養但又驚比人投訴會害左隻狗<br />\n但之前見隔離屋都有養"},{"pid":"f449b2b974c9dd7fe4c58950bbda91f320f4285b","tid":1094920,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5da2bfd28eed82fcfa1d8c0dca53ae08641ff30","tid":1094920,"uid":202044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:22:24.000Z","msg":"因為小弟好中意狗想養但又驚比人投訴會害左隻狗<br />\n但之前見隔離屋都有養"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T07:21:14.000Z","msg":"養細狗就得"},{"pid":"7b1cf017e020ecdce6e139c346ffbd1c604873d5","tid":1094920,"uid":106165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5da2bfd28eed82fcfa1d8c0dca53ae08641ff30","tid":1094920,"uid":202044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:22:24.000Z","msg":"因為小弟好中意狗想養但又驚比人投訴會害左隻狗<br />\n但之前見隔離屋都有養"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T07:22:38.000Z","msg":"唔好搞啦<br />\n一陣比人投訴咁你隻狗點算"},{"pid":"aa95c437d0229845a811095ad60566b1b1e8c44a","tid":1094920,"uid":198541,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5da2bfd28eed82fcfa1d8c0dca53ae08641ff30","tid":1094920,"uid":202044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:22:24.000Z","msg":"因為小弟好中意狗想養但又驚比人投訴會害左隻狗<br />\n但之前見隔離屋都有養"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:58:54.000Z","msg":"停一停諗一諗,唔好害狗pls"},{"pid":"3aa1e878eebdf5faff2e7aa815688def403f271f","tid":1094920,"uid":39600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c5da2bfd28eed82fcfa1d8c0dca53ae08641ff30","tid":1094920,"uid":202044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:22:24.000Z","msg":"因為小弟好中意狗想養但又驚比人投訴會害左隻狗<br />\n但之前見隔離屋都有養"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T1